      | player   | correct item | correct quantity | correct world | wrong item | wrong quantity | wrong world |
      | Kiran    | orange       | 4                | 2             | apple      | 2              | 1           |
      | Stella   | apple        | 2                | 1             | orange     | 4              | 2           |

